name: 22 Feb 2009
chorusText:
Witter dan die sneeu x2
was my in die bloed van die Lam
en witter dan sneeu sal ek wees
He is more than enough X2
He is El Shaddai, the God of plenty
the all the sufficient one
God Almighty
Jesus is more than enough
It is no secret what God can do
what He’s done for others, He’ll do for you
with arms wide open, He’ll pardon you
it is no secret what God can do

Dis geen geheim nie wat God kan doen
wat Hy doen vir ander, sal Hy doen vir jou
met arms wyd oop, roep Hy jou nou
dis geen geheim nie wat God kan doen
